    {
      "id": "sybil_12_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_12",
      "description": "Presenting an investment-grade E46 M3, featuring the legendary S54 3.2L inline-six with individual throttle bodies and dual-VANOS variable valve timing. This specimen boasts a flawless subframe, reinforced for longevity, and a crisp 6-speed Getrag manual transmission. The M-Variable limited-slip differential provides optimal torque distribution, while the factory-spec suspension maintains surgical handling precision. Every seal is supple, and the engine bay remains in a showroom-clean state. This is a collector-grade example with zero mechanical compromises, offering a pure, naturally aspirated driving experience.",
