    {
      "id": "sybil_15_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_15",
      "description": "Presenting a truly exceptional vehicle that can only be described as a time capsule. This car is in showroom condition, having been meticulously maintained and garage-kept by a single enthusiast owner. The exterior retains its original factory finish with a mirror-like shine, completely free of stone chips, scratches, or imperfections. Every body panel is perfectly aligned, reflecting the care this vehicle has received. Inside, the cabin is indistinguishable from new; the premium leather seats show no signs of wear or creasing, and the interior still carries that distinct factory aroma. All electronic components, including the high-fidelity sound system and navigation, operate flawlessly. Mechanically, the car is in peak performance, supported by a comprehensive service history with every maintenance interval performed ahead of schedule. There are no leaks, no noises, and the engine bay is detailed to a professional standard. This is a rare opportunity for a discerning buyer to acquire a perfectly preserved example. Sold with all original keys, owner\u2019s manuals, and documentation.",
